Sentencas: The cobalt for protective layer on SUS430 steel was firstly deposited by electroplating, and La0.6Sr0.4CoO3-delta for cathode contact layer was then prepared by screen printing.
Titulo: Fabrication and Property of Co3O4 and La0.6Sr0.4CoO3-δ Dual Layer Coatings on SUS430 Steel

Sentencas: Co3O4 was used as sintering additives to improve sintering behavior of the contact layer.
Titulo: Fabrication and Property of Co3O4 and La0.6Sr0.4CoO3-δ Dual Layer Coatings on SUS430 Steel

Sentencas: Dual layer coatings Co3O4 and La0.6Sr0.4CoO3-delta were formed by subsequent oxidation at 800 degrees C in air.
Titulo: Fabrication and Property of Co3O4 and La0.6Sr0.4CoO3-δ Dual Layer Coatings on SUS430 Steel

Sentencas: The phases, morphology and element diffusion of the dual layer coatings were analyzed by XRD, SEM and EDS.
Titulo: Fabrication and Property of Co3O4 and La0.6Sr0.4CoO3-δ Dual Layer Coatings on SUS430 Steel

Sentencas: The results show that the dual layer coatings achieve good bonding and adhesion, and effectively block chromium diffusion.
Titulo: Fabrication and Property of Co3O4 and La0.6Sr0.4CoO3-δ Dual Layer Coatings on SUS430 Steel

Sentencas: The interconnect with dual layer coatings exhibits a low ASR value of 23 m Omega.cm(2) after isothermal oxidation at 800 degrees C for 200 h. The dual layer coatings effectively improve the oxidation resistance and electrical properties of SUS430 steel substrate.
Titulo: Fabrication and Property of Co3O4 and La0.6Sr0.4CoO3-δ Dual Layer Coatings on SUS430 Steel
